to overcome habits of porn use on Tuesdays, 8-10 pm in Cathedral Place (803 
Terry Ave). All are welcome. <i>Information</i>,
<a href="mailto:tfrasene@stjames-cathedral.org?subject=Anti-Pornography Support Group">
Tom Frasene</a>.</p>

<p><b>NIGHTWATCH TEAM NEEDS VOLUNTEERS!</b> The St.
